# E-SYSTEM Programming Rules (2024-06-19)
- Hierarchy: P.A.R.A. (00_SOPORTE, 01_SRC, 02_TESTS, 03_DOCS, 04_ASSETS)
- Nomenclature: CLAW_YYYY_MM_DD_DESCRIPTION_VXX.py
- Independence: Config in 00_SOPORTE, Logic in 01_SRC.
- Security: Log 'alerta de enfriamiento' if > 50 mins.
- IA: Sage (qwen2.5:0.5b) coordinates. Claude EXCLUDED.
